data.description: Welcome home to a beautifully upgraded ranch that is a must see.  This home has an open floor plan and a primary bedroom with a massive attached full bath.  The home was recently painted and new flooring was installed throughout the home which includes new carpet in bedrooms and LVP in all other living spaces.  This home is move in ready.  Schedule your appointment to see this beautiful home.
